{"tid":1763243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今個週未，香港再次平靜，太好了","createTime":"2019-11-30T07:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T08:17:16.000Z","uid":51615,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3818551b6fafcf512fbc5de218060b33ce121cf1","tid":1763243,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"一切得來不易，沒有仇恨，沒有暴力，沒有tg，香港終於回到從前了"},{"pid":"75bfec1f380f76fc5f9cccacc1c6c85cf70bbc44","tid":1763243,"uid":198590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:39:02.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#51615 - 緊火</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span>, 請大家多加注意, 善用不推文回覆！<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>今日已經十一月三號，唔夠個半月就平安夜... - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>各大商場，零聖誕報置，零氣氛，往年尖東同海港城，已經完成聖誕報置準備亮登啦！<br />\n<br />\n今年... 乜都無哂<br />\n<br />\n今年，香港的聖誕節，可能是自二次大戰香港淪陷後第二個黑色聖誕...<br />\n<br />\n香港，我既家，點解會搞成咁！</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1693062/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1693062/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>有好多偏黃有小小中立fd，睇完今朝林鄭講話，立場開始軟化 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>一臉苦口婆心咁講，唔好咁執著，特首都認哂低威，不如放過大家，放過香港，俾香港一條生路 。。。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1300018/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1300018/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>見到林鄭剛才一臉憔悴，這個星期必定很不好受，她的道歉，我接受了 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>大家一人退一步好嗎</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1239751/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1239751/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>政府高層深夜急召會議 林鄭料今宣布暫緩修例 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>階段勝利，終於可以鬆番一口氣！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2019464-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E6%80%A5%E5%8F%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0+%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2019464-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%25A4%259C%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%258F%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%2B%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipfy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=7af35e7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2019464-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%25A4%259C%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%258F%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%2B%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B&h=1b0a023e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2019464-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E6%80%A5%E5%8F%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0+%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n星島日報報道）政府原定在今年七月前完成《逃犯條例》修訂草案審議，惹來反對派連番發動遊行示威阻撓，甚至釀成暴力衝突。據悉，專責香港事務的中央港澳協調小組組長韓正近日南下深圳，並曾與特首林鄭月娥商討事件。而林鄭在衡量各種因素後，決定暫緩修例，重新諮詢。林鄭昨晚深夜召開全體司局長會議，商討有關決定，並會在今早會晤全體建制派議員交代決定及作出解釋，然後即會向公眾作出宣布。消息人士表示，今次決定是希望有關《逃犯條例》的修訂能夠回歸理性，讓政府有時間聽取民意，</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1223899/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1223899/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>六九真係好煩，要諗咁多既 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>又要睇隔離左右自後係咪鬼<br />\n又話要醒目<br />\n又話要分柝型勢<br />\n<br />\n大佬啊，我毅進仔咋，點同一時間處理咁多野<br />\n<br />\n好煩，壓力好大，六九遊行，都係不了</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1190576/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1190576/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"27f11ba9263432dfee815150c12f88de510c3f59","tid":1763243,"uid":152340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:41:45.000Z","msg":"樓主，屌你老母"},{"pid":"b1b71f919ffac9774178e893b023b93d0ac89522","tid":1763243,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"成班連登仔只為區選，無眼睇"}]}